msgid "If you're willing to use an external device, attach your storage device"
msgstr ""

#: ../../storage.rst:20 260b8dc9be714661b32bb83e16fca195
msgid "Access the ``Storage`` page under the ``System`` section on the right menu"
msgstr ""

#: ../../storage.rst:21 4ce45d35a72645de8a29ceaf6fbf23c2
msgid "Select the desired storage where logs will be written to"
msgstr ""

#: ../../storage.rst:22 d5f4964add7a4e998ed7ed532762af46
msgid "Click on button :guilabel:`Format and configure storage`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../storage.rst:24 2a607fdde3354ea58b3426d8075a7901
msgid ""
"If the chosen device is the primary disk, the system will generate a new "
"partition utilizing any unallocated space. In the case of an additional "
"disk selection, the system will undertake the preparation process, which "
"involves erasing all existing partitions and data on the selected device,"
" resulting in the creation of a one single partition."
msgstr ""

#: ../../storage.rst:28 bf121a973e4a4e3f94a388d35ed0d36a
msgid ""
"In both cases, the partition will be formatted using the ext4 filesystem "
"and mounted as storage at ``/mnt/data``."
msgstr ""

